name: Rapid Recipes
body:
### Stay hungry.
We are developing a program that will find you a recipe based on the foods in your pantry, the amount of time you want to spend cooking, and your favorite ethnic cuisines.  We hope you will enjoy.

### Designers
Anisha Nakagawa, Maggie Jakus, and Annabel Consilvio are developing this program.  They attend Olin College of Engineering.

### Project Proposal
Find our project proposal [here](https://render.githubusercontent.com/view/pdf?commit=13ea047dffaa3337b9d8178b2f65d6f1c66300bf&nwo=aconsilvio%2Frecipe_program&path=SoftdesProjectProposal.pdf&url=https%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Faconsilvio%2Frecipe_program%2Fmaster%2FSoftdesProjectProposal.pdf#a28163c8-be40-4d02-9bfe-c2a8b97740ef).
